{
  "stem": "21652.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My sister, who was perhaps 17 years of age now, went to Moniek Merin, who was the head of the Jewish Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Germans assigned Jews to rule over Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And somehow, it was like a miracle happened, that they sent my brother home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Eliezar was sent home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Little did we know then that it was a bad decision.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Had he stayed in camp, he would have had chances of survival.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the fact that he came home, he was later taken away to Auschwitz or Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We're not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember Simon's DP camp was [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the other brothers, I-- I'm-- I don't recall the name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after the end of the war, we were reunited with Nathan and Itzak in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We still kept on practicing religion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Without a father, it was different, completely different.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And naturally, the Sabbath was still observed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And candles were lit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother was a very, very brave lady.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she tried to keep the family the way-- the best way she could.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Later on, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my sisters had to work, they-- two of my sisters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were taken to work in Sosnowiec sewing uniforms for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, I didn't have to go to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one day, they didn't come home from work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were told that they were taken to a concentration camp from work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the time, we didn't have any news from the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But a few weeks later, the Gestapo or S-- SS men was knocking very hard on our door in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was sleeping with my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they told me to get dressed fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took me away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
